{"type":null,"faqId":46346,"title":"Huawei Watch_How can I clean and care for my watch?","answer":"<a name=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757469\"></a><a name=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757469\"></a><div id=\"body1442371814970\"><p id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757469__p39831408175053\">Keep the watch and your wrist clean and dry and wipe off any sweat after you have finished exercising. Clean the watch regularly by wiping it with a soft cloth and remove any dirt lodged in nooks and crannies.</p><p id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0019757469__p22938353175053\">With a stainless steel mesh strap, do not forcibly bend the strap, as this may cause irreparable damage.</p></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div>","faqTypeId":591,"faqType":"Product Maintenance","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"en-us_topic_0019757469","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Product-Maintenance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444636884000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":54,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"clean, care","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}